33
00:01:56.548 --> 00:01:58.888
we're working hard to make sure everything goes without a hitch.

34
00:01:59.061 --> 00:02:02.181
Well. I'm sure whoever last updated MTAC back in the '90s

35
00:02:02.355 --> 00:02:03.871
worked hard. too. but that

36
00:02:04.174 --> 00:02:05.647
hasn't stopped hackers from exploiting our weaknesses.

37
00:02:05.820 --> 00:02:07.814
And. apparently. that was due to a delay

38
00:02:07.987 --> 00:02:09.374
