39
00:02:09.547 --> 00:02:11.150
and we are working hard to prevent that. too.

40
00:02:11.324 --> 00:02:13.447
Look. I hate to be such a hard-ass. but

41
00:02:13.707 --> 00:02:15.136
since this upgrade date was potentially leaked.

42
00:02:15.311 --> 00:02:16.827
we can't be too careful.

43
00:02:17.130 --> 00:02:18.907
Which is precisely why we're no longer doing that date

44
00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:20.467
