- in case you needed moral support. - Yeah.

59
00:02:47.851 --> 00:02:49.584
- But I-I don't want to interrupt. - No. you're not.

60
00:02:49.758 --> 00:02:52.228
Special Agent Parker. this is David Barbado.

61
00:02:52.401 --> 00:02:54.785
- DoD. - Deputy Chief of Cyber Security.

62
00:02:54.958 --> 00:02:56.864
- Hi. Oh. sorry. - Parker.

63
00:02:57.038 --> 00:02:58.424
Glad you're here to help.

64
00:02:58.598 --> 00:02:59.768
What? No.

65
00:03:00.027 --> 00:03:01.588
Uh. no. Kasie doesn't need my help.

66
00:03:01.761 --> 00:03:03.927
that's for sure. Between her and her cyber team.

67
00:03:04.187 --> 00:03:06.397
MTAC couldn't be in better hands.

68
00:03:06.571 --> 00:03:08.520
That's exactly what we're counting on. so

69
00:03:08.780 --> 00:03:11.034
I will leave you to it. then. Miss Hines.

70
00:03:11.207 --> 00:03:13.027
And just remember...

71
00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:15.800
