72
00:03:15.973 --> 00:03:18.313
So. best of luck.

73
00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:22.516
Barbado out.

74
00:03:25.029 --> 00:03:26.719
"Barbado out"?

75
00:03:26.892 --> 00:03:28.582
Dude. I was this close to convincing him

76
00:03:28.756 --> 00:03:30.099
