81
00:03:39.978 --> 00:03:42.881
Eh. how about some good old-fashioned donuts?

82
00:03:43.055 --> 00:03:45.785
- Little. uh. emergency sugar rush couldn't hurt. - Mm-mm.

83
00:03:45.958 --> 00:03:48.948
Mm-mm. No. no. no. Please do not say emergency. No. Not tonight.

84
00:03:49.121 --> 00:03:52.154
Uh. you heard what Mr. DoD Cyber Security said.

85
00:03:52.328 --> 00:03:54.624
But you heard what I said. Look. I know that. uh.

86
00:03:54.797 --> 00:03:57.138
rebooting our whole entire system here is a big job.

87
00:03:57.311 --> 00:03:59.564
but you and your tech trolls are up to it.

88
00:03:59.737 --> 00:04:01.513
Yeah. my tech trolls. Don't I wish.

89
00:04:01.686 --> 00:04:02.683
What. they're not?

90
00:04:02.857 --> 00:04:04.676
Well. for security purposes.

91
00:04:04.850 --> 00:04:08.056
DoD assigned me cyber techs from four separate agencies.

92
00:04:08.230 --> 00:04:09.920
All very highly qualified. but man.

93
00:04:10.093 --> 00:04:12.129
